text:
Scotch Presbyterian Church, Central Park West at S.W. corner of 96th Street. This structure was demolished in the fall of 1928 to make way for an apartment house. July 10, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 96th Street
